1
00:00:13,010 --> 00:00:15,810
[Episode 22]

2
00:00:16,046 --> 00:00:19,699
[Zhou's residence]

3
00:00:25,492 --> 00:00:26,691
What's going on in this mansion?

4
00:00:27,132 --> 00:00:28,051
Fifth Concubine.

5
00:00:28,052 --> 00:00:28,931
Ms. Ye.

6
00:00:29,252 --> 00:00:30,611
Third Concubine...

7
00:00:30,972 --> 00:00:33,051
she hanged herself last night.

8
00:00:33,412 --> 00:00:34,331
Suicide?

9
00:00:37,572 --> 00:00:38,411
Master.

10
00:00:38,572 --> 00:00:40,331
After all the wicked things she did,

11
00:00:40,532 --> 00:00:42,131
you're still building a memorial hall for her.

12
00:00:42,492 --> 00:00:43,771
If she could know in the afterlife,

13
00:00:44,572 --> 00:00:45,851
she'd have no regrets.

14
00:00:46,532 --> 00:00:48,531
I wanted her to live peacefully,

15
00:00:48,612 --> 00:00:50,451
never thought she'd take her own life.

16
00:00:50,692 --> 00:00:51,291
That day,

17
00:00:51,452 --> 00:00:53,051
when I delivered things to the cold courtyard,

18
00:00:53,652 --> 00:00:54,931
I didn't notice anything

19
00:00:55,172 --> 00:00:56,371
to suggest she was troubled.

20
00:00:56,372 --> 00:00:57,731
She had a good place to go.

21
00:00:58,132 --> 00:00:59,651
Why would Third Concubine commit suicide?

22
00:01:00,612 --> 00:01:01,331
Why are you here?

23
00:01:04,492 --> 00:01:05,331
Ms. Ye,

24
00:01:05,532 --> 00:01:07,251
we found this suicide note

25
00:01:07,372 --> 00:01:08,531
beside Third Concubine's body.

26
00:01:08,972 --> 00:01:10,091
It says essentially,

27
00:01:10,972 --> 00:01:12,731
with both Master and Second Young Master dead,

28
00:01:12,972 --> 00:01:14,651
she refuses to return home to end her days,

29
00:01:15,132 --> 00:01:16,331
so she followed them.

30
00:01:17,372 --> 00:01:18,611
I need to speak with you.

31
00:01:18,692 --> 00:01:19,291
Master,

32
00:01:19,292 --> 00:01:20,171
I'll take my leave.

33
00:01:24,252 --> 00:01:24,971
What's wrong?

34
00:01:25,212 --> 00:01:26,211
You seem worried.

35
00:01:28,772 --> 00:01:30,171
I just received a letter

36
00:01:30,172 --> 00:01:32,011
from Xu Hansheng at the mansion gate.

37
00:01:33,692 --> 00:01:34,291
Xu...

38
00:01:34,292 --> 00:01:35,171
Xu Hansheng?

39
00:01:35,732 --> 00:01:36,691
Isn't he dead?

40
00:01:36,692 --> 00:01:37,531
He must have arranged

41
00:01:37,532 --> 00:01:38,851
to have the letter sent beforehand.

42
00:01:39,372 --> 00:01:40,251
The letter says,

43
00:01:40,412 --> 00:01:41,971
after he sexually assaulted my sister,

44
00:01:42,052 --> 00:01:43,531
he confirmed she wasn't dead.

45
00:01:44,492 --> 00:01:46,331
He wrote to tell you

46
00:01:46,732 --> 00:01:48,291
that someone else pushed your sister

47
00:01:48,292 --> 00:01:49,171
into the lake.

48
00:01:49,812 --> 00:01:51,171
Is it possible

49
00:01:51,852 --> 00:01:53,931
someone forged a letter in Ye Chuxue's name

50
00:01:54,212 --> 00:01:55,371
to write this letter?

51
00:01:55,652 --> 00:01:56,611
Luring your sister

52
00:01:57,212 --> 00:01:58,131
and the steward

53
00:01:58,212 --> 00:01:59,411
to the back garden simultaneously.

54
00:01:59,412 --> 00:02:00,691
Kill my sister

55
00:02:01,572 --> 00:02:02,811
and frame the steward.

56
00:02:03,252 --> 00:02:04,251
The letter says,

57
00:02:04,532 --> 00:02:06,131
the invitation letter is well-preserved.

58
00:02:06,492 --> 00:02:08,091
But we've searched his room thoroughly

59
00:02:08,092 --> 00:02:09,131
and found nothing.

60
00:02:09,652 --> 00:02:10,251
Let's go.

61
00:02:10,852 --> 00:02:11,651
Let's check again!

62
00:02:13,692 --> 00:02:15,491
This place is practically empty.

63
00:02:15,612 --> 00:02:16,691
Where would we find any letters?

64
00:02:26,292 --> 00:02:27,091
Did you find it?

65
00:02:32,732 --> 00:02:35,291
The Golden Lotus?

66
00:02:36,612 --> 00:02:38,171
You haven't read this book, have you?

67
00:02:38,492 --> 00:02:39,531
- I have!
- It's about...

68
00:02:40,212 --> 00:02:41,211
Read it at a used book stall.

69
00:02:43,972 --> 00:02:44,411
You...

70
00:02:44,732 --> 00:02:46,571
You... an educated woman...

71
00:02:47,492 --> 00:02:48,491
Reading such books?

72
00:02:48,492 --> 00:02:49,211
What's wrong with that?

73
00:02:49,852 --> 00:02:51,291
I'm educated, not a nun.

74
00:02:51,532 --> 00:02:52,531
Should only men read this?

75
00:02:52,612 --> 00:02:53,731
Are women not allowed?

76
00:02:54,852 --> 00:02:56,771
Women have curiosity too, you know.

77
00:03:00,572 --> 00:03:01,371
That makes sense.

78
00:03:11,612 --> 00:03:13,491
I've admired you for a long time.

79
00:03:14,332 --> 00:03:15,811
I wish to invite you tonight

80
00:03:16,172 --> 00:03:17,571
for a meeting at the back hill.

81
00:03:18,612 --> 00:03:19,491
Admired?

82
00:03:19,932 --> 00:03:21,691
How could she like that beast?

83
00:03:22,412 --> 00:03:23,691
Back when she was still here,

84
00:03:23,932 --> 00:03:24,851
she always kept her distance

85
00:03:24,852 --> 00:03:25,971
from steward Xu.

86
00:03:26,292 --> 00:03:27,611
But this handwriting...

87
00:03:29,932 --> 00:03:32,131
Why is it identical to my sister's?

88
00:03:39,932 --> 00:03:41,771
All who worked in the manor three years ago

89
00:03:41,772 --> 00:03:42,811
and were literate-

90
00:03:44,052 --> 00:03:45,411
all their handwriting samples are here.

91
00:03:46,132 --> 00:03:46,811
Not a single person's

92
00:03:46,812 --> 00:03:48,611
matches Ye Chuixue's handwriting.

93
00:03:51,572 --> 00:03:52,691
This handwriting...

94
00:03:54,892 --> 00:03:56,451
I feel like I've seen it somewhere before.

95
00:04:00,772 --> 00:04:02,051
Third Concubine's suicide note.

96
00:04:05,172 --> 00:04:05,731
Here.

97
00:04:10,132 --> 00:04:11,371
Completely different!

98
00:04:11,932 --> 00:04:13,131
A person's handwriting

99
00:04:13,612 --> 00:04:14,851
has consistent stroke proportions,

100
00:04:15,252 --> 00:04:16,531
writing movement patterns,

101
00:04:16,732 --> 00:04:17,931
forming a coherent system.

102
00:04:18,172 --> 00:04:19,531
The character "Home" in Third Concubine's note

103
00:04:20,092 --> 00:04:21,571
compared to this "home" in my sister's letter-

104
00:04:22,212 --> 00:04:23,291
uneven slant,

105
00:04:23,572 --> 00:04:24,771
inconsistent stroke speed,

106
00:04:24,932 --> 00:04:25,851
unnatural movement,

107
00:04:26,372 --> 00:04:27,331
awkward turns.

108
00:04:27,692 --> 00:04:29,411
Yet both characters strictly follow

109
00:04:29,812 --> 00:04:31,891
the Slender Gold style conventions.

110
00:04:32,292 --> 00:04:33,611
This means Third Concubine's note

111
00:04:34,292 --> 00:04:35,931
was written by the same person as my sister's letter,

112
00:04:36,412 --> 00:04:37,491
but deliberately disguised.

113
00:04:37,612 --> 00:04:38,371
Therefore,

114
00:04:38,732 --> 00:04:40,811
Third Concubine's suicide note is also forged.

115
00:04:43,892 --> 00:04:44,931
It seems my sister's death

116
00:04:45,972 --> 00:04:47,211
and Third Concubine's death

117
00:04:47,932 --> 00:04:49,491
were both committed by the same killer.

118
00:04:51,412 --> 00:04:52,651
And they're right here in this manor.

119
00:04:57,612 --> 00:04:58,851
Regarding the shop lease renewals,

120
00:04:59,092 --> 00:05:00,171
I must trouble you all

121
00:05:00,172 --> 00:05:01,091
for your assistance.

122
00:05:04,092 --> 00:05:04,891
Ms. Ye,

123
00:05:05,172 --> 00:05:06,051
are you looking for the Master?

124
00:05:06,572 --> 00:05:07,091
No.

125
00:05:07,452 --> 00:05:08,211
I came to find you.

126
00:05:08,372 --> 00:05:09,211
Are you busy?

127
00:05:10,172 --> 00:05:11,011
Me?

128
00:05:12,532 --> 00:05:13,451
My apologies, everyone.

129
00:05:13,772 --> 00:05:14,811
This is an important guest.

130
00:05:15,292 --> 00:05:16,371
I must excuse myself momentarily.

131
00:05:23,532 --> 00:05:24,931
Our judgment was indeed correct.

132
00:05:25,692 --> 00:05:27,251
You excel at managing household affairs.

133
00:05:28,492 --> 00:05:29,291
Thank you for your trust,

134
00:05:29,412 --> 00:05:30,651
Ms. Ye and Master.

135
00:05:31,092 --> 00:05:32,131
What brings you to me?

136
00:05:32,532 --> 00:05:34,131
Do you have any records of household affairs

137
00:05:34,492 --> 00:05:35,491
written by Third Concubine

138
00:05:35,492 --> 00:05:36,491
during her time managing the household?

139
00:05:38,212 --> 00:05:39,171
Well...

140
00:05:39,532 --> 00:05:41,171
Master already asked me about this earlier.

141
00:05:41,652 --> 00:05:43,691
Third Concubine rarely wrote herself.

142
00:05:43,932 --> 00:05:44,811
The household records

143
00:05:44,812 --> 00:05:46,891
were transcribed by the steward and me.

144
00:05:47,332 --> 00:05:48,051
Why

145
00:05:48,052 --> 00:05:49,371
do you need them so urgently?

146
00:05:52,492 --> 00:05:53,411
Never mind then.

147
00:05:54,172 --> 00:05:54,891
Ms. Ye,

148
00:05:55,092 --> 00:05:56,131
I just remembered...

149
00:05:56,412 --> 00:05:58,411
When the Third Concubine first married into the household,

150
00:05:58,412 --> 00:05:59,411
she really loved listening to operas.

151
00:05:59,812 --> 00:06:01,651
She used to transcribe some opera lyrics.

152
00:06:02,132 --> 00:06:03,131
They were confiscated by the Master.

153
00:06:03,412 --> 00:06:04,931
I think they're in this accounting room.

154
00:06:05,172 --> 00:06:05,731
Please wait,

155
00:06:05,732 --> 00:06:06,491
I'll find them for you.

156
00:06:06,772 --> 00:06:07,131
Okay.

157
00:06:12,212 --> 00:06:12,531
Here,

158
00:06:12,532 --> 00:06:13,371
Ms. Ye.

159
00:06:20,972 --> 00:06:22,211
Can I have these?

160
00:06:23,812 --> 00:06:24,691
Then I'll leave you to your work.

161
00:06:24,692 --> 00:06:25,491
I'll take my leave.

162
00:06:26,172 --> 00:06:27,531
Won't you wait for the Master to return?

163
00:06:28,452 --> 00:06:29,131
No, I won't wait.

164
00:06:35,092 --> 00:06:37,691
[Zhou's residence]

165
00:06:37,692 --> 00:06:38,291
Young Master,

166
00:06:38,452 --> 00:06:39,171
be careful.

167
00:06:40,292 --> 00:06:40,931
Master.

168
00:06:41,532 --> 00:06:42,131
Here,

169
00:06:42,452 --> 00:06:42,971
watch your step.

170
00:06:45,572 --> 00:06:46,611
Careful, Master!

171
00:06:46,612 --> 00:06:47,611
The Young Master drank too much today.

172
00:06:47,652 --> 00:06:48,611
He vomited all over the car.

173
00:06:49,732 --> 00:06:50,371
You two,

174
00:06:50,492 --> 00:06:51,851
help Jinbao clean the car.

175
00:06:51,852 --> 00:06:52,771
I'll take care of the Master.

176
00:06:52,932 --> 00:06:53,851
- Yes.
- Okay.

177
00:06:53,852 --> 00:06:55,291
Then please take good care of him.

178
00:06:55,292 --> 00:06:56,051
Here, careful.

179
00:06:58,412 --> 00:06:59,051
Careful.

180
00:07:09,852 --> 00:07:12,291
The handwriting of the opera lyrics transcribed by the Third Concubine

181
00:07:12,532 --> 00:07:13,931
is identical to the suicide note.

182
00:07:14,932 --> 00:07:16,531
Could my judgment have been wrong?

183
00:07:18,332 --> 00:07:19,091
Master.

184
00:07:25,452 --> 00:07:29,371
[Zhou's residence]

185
00:07:30,212 --> 00:07:31,251
Why isn't the door closed?

186
00:07:31,812 --> 00:07:33,251
Look what tasty food I brought you.

187
00:07:34,052 --> 00:07:34,891
Zhiqiu.

188
00:07:40,252 --> 00:07:41,091
Nanxi?

189
00:07:41,252 --> 00:07:41,771
You...

190
00:07:50,132 --> 00:07:51,091
Let me explain.

191
00:07:54,692 --> 00:07:55,491
Explain then.

192
00:08:03,572 --> 00:08:04,371
I was...

193
00:08:05,132 --> 00:08:05,931
drunk last night.

194
00:08:07,452 --> 00:08:09,451
Jinbao drove me back.

195
00:08:09,452 --> 00:08:10,051
Yes.

196
00:08:10,052 --> 00:08:11,771
Jinbao drove me back.

197
00:08:12,412 --> 00:08:13,611
He dropped me off at the door.

198
00:08:14,852 --> 00:08:15,411
I...

199
00:08:24,652 --> 00:08:25,931
My head hurts too much.

200
00:08:27,052 --> 00:08:28,131
I don't remember much.

201
00:08:28,772 --> 00:08:29,891
I passed out from the pain.

202
00:08:32,412 --> 00:08:33,491
Passed out from the pain?

203
00:08:36,092 --> 00:08:37,291
Who changed your clothes?

204
00:08:41,452 --> 00:08:43,291
Why was Nanxi in your bed?

205
00:08:43,852 --> 00:08:44,771
Ms. Ye.

206
00:08:45,372 --> 00:08:46,211
Don't misunderstand.

207
00:08:47,052 --> 00:08:48,051
Last night's incident...

208
00:08:48,852 --> 00:08:49,731
wasn't the Master's fault.

209
00:08:51,252 --> 00:08:51,931
Whose fault is it then?

210
00:08:52,932 --> 00:08:53,691
Mine?

211
00:08:54,652 --> 00:08:55,411
It's my fault.

212
00:08:56,532 --> 00:08:57,851
The Master was drunk last night.

213
00:08:58,412 --> 00:08:59,811
He mistook me for you.

214
00:09:00,532 --> 00:09:01,051
I...

215
00:09:02,332 --> 00:09:03,051
didn't refuse.

216
00:09:03,052 --> 00:09:03,931
Shut up!

217
00:09:05,772 --> 00:09:06,531
Master.

218
00:09:08,492 --> 00:09:09,491
So you knew

219
00:09:09,732 --> 00:09:11,011
he thought you were me,

220
00:09:11,732 --> 00:09:12,931
and you didn't refuse.

221
00:09:13,612 --> 00:09:14,451
Nanxi.

222
00:09:15,852 --> 00:09:16,691
As fellow women,

223
00:09:17,412 --> 00:09:19,091
I wanted to protect your reputation.

224
00:09:20,172 --> 00:09:21,851
But it seems I was worried for nothing.

225
00:09:22,892 --> 00:09:23,811
Ms. Ye.

226
00:09:24,452 --> 00:09:25,251
Don't go.

227
00:09:25,812 --> 00:09:26,251
I...

228
00:09:27,252 --> 00:09:28,051
I'm leaving.

229
00:09:28,652 --> 00:09:29,771
If you leave,

230
00:09:30,292 --> 00:09:31,411
you'll have nothing left.

231
00:09:31,412 --> 00:09:32,571
It'll all be in vain.

232
00:09:37,532 --> 00:09:38,251
Master!

233
00:09:38,812 --> 00:09:40,571
I beg you, not to leave me with nothing.

234
00:09:41,052 --> 00:09:42,531
I've followed you all this way,

235
00:09:42,532 --> 00:09:43,291
building this empire,

236
00:09:43,292 --> 00:09:44,411
protecting this legacy.

237
00:09:44,412 --> 00:09:45,891
I've worked hard, if nothing else.

238
00:09:45,892 --> 00:09:47,891
Don't leave me with nothing, Master.

239
00:09:47,892 --> 00:09:48,531
Let go.

240
00:09:48,732 --> 00:09:49,291
Zhiqiu.

241
00:09:49,292 --> 00:09:50,171
Don't follow me.

242
00:09:53,652 --> 00:09:55,411
[Zhongshan Hospital]

243
00:09:55,452 --> 00:09:56,571
So these past few days,

244
00:09:57,092 --> 00:09:57,891
she hasn't come.

245
00:09:58,452 --> 00:09:59,131
Right.

246
00:09:59,652 --> 00:10:00,691
Took a few days off.

247
00:10:03,852 --> 00:10:05,091
No one's in the dorm either.

248
00:10:06,532 --> 00:10:07,811
I was about to call the police.

249
00:10:07,892 --> 00:10:09,291
That's not necessary.

250
00:10:09,892 --> 00:10:10,691
Maybe...

251
00:10:10,892 --> 00:10:12,211
she's avoiding you on purpose.

252
00:10:12,652 --> 00:10:13,291
Perhaps,

253
00:10:13,292 --> 00:10:14,611
giving each other some space

254
00:10:15,412 --> 00:10:16,251
would allow

255
00:10:16,652 --> 00:10:17,811
more room for maneuver.

256
00:10:20,772 --> 00:10:21,371
Director!

257
00:10:21,532 --> 00:10:22,811
Several patients are getting impatient.

258
00:10:23,092 --> 00:10:23,891
Mr. Zhou.

259
00:10:24,172 --> 00:10:25,051
My apologies.

260
00:10:26,332 --> 00:10:27,171
Director Lin,

261
00:10:27,772 --> 00:10:28,691
I'll be going now.

262
00:10:28,892 --> 00:10:29,931
If you see her,

263
00:10:30,612 --> 00:10:31,611
please tell her,

264
00:10:32,772 --> 00:10:34,331
I'll wait for her to change her mind.

265
00:10:35,452 --> 00:10:35,931
Okay.

266
00:10:52,092 --> 00:10:53,091
You can come out now.

267
00:11:02,772 --> 00:11:04,251
Hiding from him all the time

268
00:11:04,652 --> 00:11:05,691
isn't good.

269
00:11:07,452 --> 00:11:08,291
Thank you, Director Lin.

270
00:11:11,172 --> 00:11:12,291
These flowers are from him.

271
00:11:16,692 --> 00:11:20,051
[Zhou's residence]

272
00:12:13,092 --> 00:12:14,291
That's right.

273
00:12:15,732 --> 00:12:17,211
This is the real you.

274
00:12:18,892 --> 00:12:19,651
Nanxi,

275
00:12:21,452 --> 00:12:23,451
you were born to be a master.

276
00:12:30,532 --> 00:12:31,971
The Third Concubine's suicide note has

277
00:12:32,332 --> 00:12:34,411
the same handwriting as the opera lyrics she copied.

278
00:12:35,772 --> 00:12:36,451
Could it be...

279
00:12:43,612 --> 00:12:44,091
Hello?

280
00:12:44,372 --> 00:12:46,251
Master Li at 17 Shucheng Road is critically ill!

281
00:12:46,252 --> 00:12:47,771
Urgent situation requiring immediate house call!

282
00:12:48,892 --> 00:12:49,971
I'm coming right now.

283
00:12:50,852 --> 00:12:52,731
I'm the on-duty doctor from Zhongshan Hospital.

284
00:12:52,852 --> 00:12:54,091
Inside, please. Come in.

285
00:13:02,532 --> 00:13:03,571
I guessed right.

286
00:13:11,212 --> 00:13:12,051
You're at the hospital.

287
00:13:19,532 --> 00:13:20,411
I came for a house call.

288
00:13:22,252 --> 00:13:23,531
Since there's no patient here,

289
00:13:24,532 --> 00:13:25,891
I have no reason to stay.

290
00:13:26,932 --> 00:13:27,611
Wait!

291
00:13:28,652 --> 00:13:29,691
I just want to see you.

292
